    <section id="story">
      <h2 class="section-title">What is The Game With No Name?</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">A fast-paced multiplayer western shooter game where every shot matters. Pick up weapons from around the map and use them to fight your enemies in different ways. Each weapon includes different perks, making you have to pick your tool for fighting.</p>
      <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap:18px;" class="mt-3">
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="mb-1">Built For Multiplayer</h3>
          <p>High skill ceiling allows for different play styles. Each bullet counts, letting you slow down your enemies by shooting them in the leg, mess up their aim by shooting them in the arm, knocking off their hat by shooting right above their head, and draining all their health by aiming for the brain or heart.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="mb-1">Physics That Allows For Chaos</h3>
          <p>Throw objects into the street, take a ride on a traincar, or use the shotgun knockback to your advantage. There's never a dull moment in this game.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="mb-1">Expertly Designed Maps</h3>
          <p>Each map has hallways, buildings, and other settings that let you get into an intense fight. Use the map to your advantage and show your enemies you know the land the best.</p>
        </article>
